<section id="mainFooterWrapper" class="universalPadding"> <div class="mainWrapper"> <section id="mainFooterSection"> <div id="mfs-content001"> <p class="p002">A domestic worker, domestic helper or domestic servant, also called menial, is a person who works within the employer's household. Domestic helpers perform a variety of household services for an individual or a family, from providing care for children and elderly dependents to housekeeping, including cleaning and household maintenance. Other responsibilities may include cooking, laundry and ironing, shopping for food and other household errands.</p> </div><div id="mfs-content002"> <p class="p002">A-72 First Floor Road No-2, Near Diplomatic Hotel, Mahipalpur Ext. New Delhi - 110037</p> <p class="p002">011-3240 0666 +91 â€“ 8800590666, +91-8800591666 </p> <p class="p002">info@domesticforyou.com</p> <p class="p002">&copy; 2018 Domestic For You</p> </div> </section> </div> </section> <section id="promotionSection"> <p>Handcrafted with <span>&#9829;</span> by <a href="https://twitter.com/xyzricky" target="_blank">Ricky Singh</a></p> </section>